                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-85-off487 t18080914-85-crimeloc489"></join>. On the 30th of July I hung out the counterpane on a pole to dry at the two pair of stairs window; I perceived it was gone. I followed the prisoner and found it on him.</p>
               <p>Q. How soon after you missed it did you find it upon him - A No longer ago than when he went out of our door and went into the next house. I followed him and took it from him.</p>
               <p>The property produced and identified.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18080914-85-person761">
