            . I saw him pulling it off the line; he put it under his arm and walked out of doors.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I do not know any more of it than a child unborn; I was very much in liquor. Out of a joke a woman said take it and pawn it, and get some more gin.</p>
